🎥  The Content Wars: YouTube vs. Instagram Reels vs. TikTok

Situation: You want to become a tech influencer and grow your audience fast.
Debate: Which platform is best for reach, engagement, and brand-building?

🔴 Team YouTube: “Depth, credibility, and monetization.”

🟣 Team Instagram Reels: “Trends, aesthetics, and quick engagement.”

🎵 Team TikTok: “Virality, creative freedom, and algorithmic push.”
